Quake walked ot the station but as Jagged walked out and pointed his 
gun at Havotron, he smiled.  AS Tiptop flipped to his hand he fired a 
ray that would cuz Jagged to lose his balnce. Without waiting for it 
to hit he rand and threw a punch at the head of Jagged. "Never go 
against a Decepticon leader, punk"

Havotron smiled as he saw Jagged taken care of.  He turned to 
Slugsling raising his cannon.  "Slugslinger, remeber the oath, wait I 
haven't amde you take an oath," he smiled even bigger, "Make one up 
now and I will spare your worthless spark." he said hoping for osme 
amusement.
